{"tid":117632,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"沒有嘗試過的人生…謝霆鋒下一個角色競猜","createTime":"2017-02-12T11:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T05:17:48.000Z","uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70eed879e1a62345d4098646e458f4951bb1b3c7","tid":117632,"uid":12661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T11:22:37.000Z","msg":"謝霆鋒由佢俾大家認識開始，做過無數角色，列舉如下：<br />\n<br />\n謝四同大波拉個仔（同大家拜年）<br />\n孝子（幫老豆還債）<br />\nRock友<br />\n監犯<br />\n商業奇才<br />\n有情有義綠帽男<br />\n好老豆<br />\n長情情聖<br />\n影帝<br />\n廚神<br />\n<br />\n正所謂：沒有嘗試過的人生，我都想嘗試一下&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n請各位巴打絲打，俾下意見，佢人生嘅下一個角色可以做啲乜嘢呢？"},{"pid":"9953dee16b84bc56c4c4fb3bb5c1a19a61c984f7","tid":117632,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T11:25:05.000Z","msg":"其實可能佢想做陳冠希個角色"},{"pid":"c6c447edda07e4dd618fca1370cac593c2ec0e02","tid":117632,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T11:25:47.000Z","msg":"做埋真係上神枱"},{"pid":"8359519de06cc4d8fc60936915815587e9238b7c","tid":117632,"uid":56467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"人大政協嗰啲啦"},{"pid":"89b40380f6b4b4c3361420ee0f91c8b9a7b2869b","tid":117632,"uid":31602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T11:55:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實可能佢想做陳冠希個角色</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a249429f26842a612dd6237a06cddda8fa7779","tid":117632,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T11:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實可能佢想做陳冠希個角色</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<